article.headline: UC Santa Barbara 63, UC Riverside 56
article.story: SANTA BARBARA, Calif. -- James Nunnally scored 20 points and Orlando Johnson added 16 as UC Santa Barbara posted a 63-56 victory against UC Riverside on Saturday. Will Brew scored 11 points for the Gauchos (9-7, 4-2 Big West). Kyle Austin had 25 points for UC Riverside (7-10, 1-4), and Lateef McMullan added 10. Santa Barbara broke open a tie game with a 17-7 run midway through the second half. Nunnally had 11 points during the run, which gave the Gauchos a 56-46 lead with 5:28 remaining.
